    "In the ever-attender sample, the coecient is similar but more precisely estimate (Column 3).",
    "It is robust to experience controls (Column 4), party-year controls (Column 5), elastic net controls (Column 6), and all of them together (Column 7).",
    "This most demanding specication holds even when including all never-attending judges in the sample, although the coecient magnitude is smaller (Column 8).",
    "Overall, the results are consistent with a 15 percent increase in the probability of voting against labor and environmental regulation agencies after attendance at the Manne program.",
